data.text:
Carol Jackson

ELJ Drinks Ltd

https://www.ellisgin.com

Carol is the founder of ELJ Drinks Ltd who produce a range of naturally coloured, flavoured Scottish Gins, distilled in Glasgow. Their aim has been to bring fun and colour to the gin market – with two of their gins changing colour when mixer is added, and their Pink Gin has a lovely mesmerising shimmer.
